			 * 			&quot;in&quot; : &quot;inside&quot;,
			 * 			&quot;out&quot; : &quot;outside&quot;
			 * 		});
			 * // t现在包含的字符串为: 'flow-rule 1 session-limit 8000 action pass in-channel inside out-channel outside'
			 * </code></pre>
			 *
